  "exec_summary": "The European Banking Authority has issued an email alert on July 16, 2026, which may be relevant to the team's compliance and regulatory work. Meanwhile, the Markets in Crypto-Assets regulation, or MiCA, has started to take effect, with BitPay obtaining a license under the new framework, and other firms such as Coinbase, Ripple, and Hilbert Group also taking steps to comply with the regulation. The National Bank of Belgium and the Financial Services and Markets Authority should be monitoring the implementation of MiCA and its impact on the Belgian financial sector. The recent developments in MiCA licensing and supervision may require the team to review and update their compliance procedures to ensure adherence to the new regulatory requirements.",
